{"id":"rimac","name_cn":"锐马克","name_en":"Rimac","country":"克罗地亚","region":"europe","founded_year":2009,"logo":"/logos/rimac.svg","intro":"锐马克是克罗地亚电动超级跑车制造商，由Mate Rimac创立。品牌以纯电超跑技术领先全球，Nevera成为世界最快电动超跑之一。","history":[{"year":2009,"event":"Mate Rimac在克罗地亚创立Rimac Automobili"},{"year":2016,"event":"Concept_One发布，展示电动超跑潜力"},{"year":2018,"event":"保时捷入股Rimac"},{"year":2021,"event":"Nevera正式发布，0-100km/h仅1.97秒"},{"year":2023,"event":"Rimac与Bugatti合并为Bugatti Rimac"}],"official_site":"https://www.rimac-automobili.com","sources":[]}